<title>USA: DHL Airways says Riera chief info officer.</title>
<headline>DHL Airways says Riera chief info officer.</headline>
<dateline>REDWOOD CITY, California 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>DHL Airways said former Apple Computer executive Joseph Riera has joined the company as senior vice president and chief information officer.</p>
<p>Riera, 56, spent 10 years at Apple where he was most recently vice president and chief information officer, information systems and technology, the express carrier said in a statement.</p>
<p>At DHL, Riera will oversee telecommunications, technical infrastructure, business applications and EDI exchanges with customers, the carrier said. --Reuters Air Cargo Newsroom Tel +44 171 542 7706 Fax +5017</p>
